	Ice cold coffee reflects much more than you want to see.
	Green logo on cup is unrecognizable.
	=> other_items
- Behind monitor
	Many layers of thick dust hides nothing important
	if not DMM.get_bool("bullet_behind_monitor") and DMM.get_bool("Ending_One_Can_Live"):
		Wait! There is a single bullet, calliber 9mm.
		When you touched it, strange feeling of compassion went through your mind. 
